"Code Review"}],["$","meta","23",{"property":"article:tag","content":"Best Practices"}],["$","meta","24",{"property":"article:tag","content":"Team Collaboration"}],["$","meta","25",{"property":"article:tag","content":"Career"}],["$","meta","26",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","27",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Seni Code Review: Lebih dari Sekadar Mencari Bug"}],["$","meta","28",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Code review yang efektif bukan hanya tentang menemukan bug, tapi juga tentang berbagi pengetahuan dan menjaga kualitas kode jangka panjang."}],["$","meta","29",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://abyte.id/uploads/1780244668140-5iirvp.webp"}]]
